<l>eṇperuk kannalat toṇporu ḷīṟila</l>
<l>vaṇpukaḻ nāraṇaṉ ṟiṇkaḻal cērē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just join the firm ankleted feet of Nāraṇaṉ, of generous fame,</l>
<l>without end, bright wealth/meaning, of that goodness that multiplies in number.</l>
